SECURITY VULNERABILITY DISCLOSURE

If You discover a security vulnerability in the Software, please report it 
responsibly by emailing security@phishguard.com with:

- Detailed description of the vulnerability
- Steps to reproduce the issue
- Potential impact assessment
- Suggested remediation (if available)

We are committed to addressing security issues promptly and will acknowledge 
receipt within 24 hours.

